    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Well-kept, good-condition vehicle that shows nicely overall and has clearly been cared for. The exterior and interior are both in solid shape, with normal age-related wear and a few minor cosmetic imperfections, but nothing that takes away from its overall appeal. It runs and drives well, and should make a strong choice for someone looking for a clean, dependable vehicle without paying mint-condition money.",
