      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle in fair condition that should suit a buyer looking for an affordable driver rather than a pristine example. It shows noticeable cosmetic wear inside and out consistent with age and use, with blemishes, imperfections, and general signs of ownership that are apparent but not unusual for a vehicle in this category. The interior is serviceable and presentable overall, though buyers should expect wear on commonly used surfaces and trim. Overall, this is an honest, mid-level example that can still be enjoyed as-is, but it\u2019s best for someone comfortable with a vehicle that has visible age and won\u2019t be mistaken for a showpiece.",
      "price": 17900.0,
