      "description": "$46,900 - Outstanding, top-tier example that shows beautifully and should appeal to buyers looking for a truly special car. This is a mint-condition vehicle with excellent presentation throughout, the kind of car that stands out for how well it has been kept. A turn-key, highly desirable classic that\u2019s ready to enjoy and proudly show.",
