    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle offers an accessible way into reliable transportation for the right buyer. Best suited for someone who values affordability and sees the opportunity in a straightforward, usable car with room to make it their own. Priced to move and presented with transparency, it\u2019s a practical choice for commuting, a backup vehicle, or a project-minded owner.",
      "price": 5995.0,
